    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''The Poets of War,'' by Nicholas D. Kristof (column, June 11):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''The Poets of War,'' by Nicholas D. Kristof (column, June 11):</p>
        <p>Mr. Kristof and the poet contributors provide a great service in bringing us closer to those who serve in Iraq and helping us understand the impact on family, friends and community.</p>
        <p>The poems jolt us into facing the costs of war in terms of human distress, tears and agony.</p>
        <p>Victor A. Grund  Briarcliff Manor, N.Y., June 11, 2007</p>
      </block>
